tino culture.\", \"from\": 1594, \"to\": 1764, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1651, \"end\": 1657, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.004313683775049e-55, \"text\": \"Raygun\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\"}, {\"begin\": 1668, \"end\": 1678, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.9999999996343831, \"rank\": 3.65864728304566e-10, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}, {\"begin\": 1730, \"end\": 1738, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999924539225, \"rank\": 5.908200986702372e-09, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1739, \"end\": 1744, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Black_people\", \"score\": 0.9983282052043922, \"rank\": 0.0016745943735750944, \"text\": \"Black\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Black_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Black_people\"}, {\"begin\": 1749, \"end\": 1755, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Music_of_Latin_America\", \"score\": 0.999999999996362, \"rank\": 3.689826034639998e-12, \"text\": \"Latino\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Music_of_Latin_America\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Music_of_Latin_America\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"accusations\", \"from\": 1610, \"to\": 1621}, {\"ngram\": \"cultural appropriation\", \"from\": 1625, \"to\": 1647}, {\"ngram\": \"breaking\", \"from\": 1701, \"to\": 1709}, {\"ngram\": \"roots\", \"from\": 1721, \"to\": 1726}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Malik Dixon, who is from New York but currently lives in Australia, told the Australian Broadcast 