n intense chapter in my breakdance life, my breaking life as a b-girl.\", \"from\": 3950, \"to\": 4043, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an intense chapter\", \"from\": 3972, \"to\": 3990}, {\"ngram\": \"my breakdance life\", \"from\": 3994, \"to\": 4012}, {\"ngram\": \"a b-girl\", \"from\": 4034, \"to\": 4042}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We had a watch party for the b-girl day, and so we were bringing the gathering, the New Yorkers and the community, to go through this moment together.\", \"from\": 4045, \"to\": 4195, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a watch party\", \"from\": 4052, \"to\": 4065}, {\"ngram\": \"the b-girl day\", \"from\": 4070, \"to\": 4084}, {\"ngram\": \"the gathering\", \"from\": 4110, \"to\": 4123}, {\"ngram\": \"the New Yorkers\", \"from\": 4125, \"to\": 4140}, {\"ngram\": \"the community\", \"from\": 4145, \"to\": 4158}, {\"ngram\": \"this moment\", \"from\": 4174, \"to\": 4185}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I tried my best to be as impartial and as open-minded as I could be, and I am still being open-minded with it.\", \"from\": 4197, \"to\": 4307, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I do wish that the world would focus more on the amazing and excellent display that all the Olympians had.\", \"from\": 4309, \"to\": 4415, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 4324, \"to\": 4333}, {\"ngram\": \"the amazing and excellent display\", \"from\": 4354, \"to\": 4387}, {\"ngram\": \"all the Olympians\", \"from\": 4393, \"to\": 4410}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You know, I feel like the medallists in each of the categories should be the ones that are being pumped up and they are not.\", \"from\": 4416, \"to\": 4540, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the medallists\", \"from\": 4438, \"to\": 4452}, {\"ngram\": \"the categories\", \"from\": 4464, \"to\": 4478}, {\"ngram\": \"the ones\", \"from\": 4489, \"to\": 4497}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And so that part is definitely frustrating, insulting, offensive, and the people who are outside of the community who are weighing in, you do not need to weigh in.\", \"from\": 4542, \"to\": 4705, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that part\", \"from\": 4549, \"to\": 4558}, {\"ngram\": \"definitely frustrating, insulting, offensive, and the people\", \"from\": 4562, \"to\": 4622}, {\"ngram\": \"the community\", \"from\": 4642, \"to\": 4655}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kwikstep: We were excited that breaking was going to be on a world stage.\", \"from\": 4707, \"to\": 4780, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"breaking\", \"from\": 4738, \"to\": 4746}, {\"ngram\": \"a world stage\", \"from\": 4766, \"to\": 4779}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am an athlete myself.\", \"from\": 4782, \"to\": 4805, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an athlete\", \"from\": 4787, \"to\": 4797}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am a tumbler.\", \"from\": 4806, \"to\": 4821, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a tumbler\", \"from\": 4811, \"to\": 4820}]}, {\"sentence\": \"An all-around gymnast.\", \"from\": 4822, \"to\": 4844, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"An all-around gymnast\", \"from\": 4822, \"to\": 4843}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I play baseball, basketball, martial arts, all of that.\", \"from\": 4845, \"to\": 4900, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"baseball\", \"from\": 4852, \"to\": 4860}, {\"ngram\": \"basketball\", \"from\": 4862, \"to\": 4872}, {\"ngram\": \"martial arts\", \"from\": 4874, \"to\": 4886}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And the best breakers I know have an athletic component to them outside of breaking.\", \"from\": 4901, \"to\": 4985, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the best breakers\", \"from\": 4905, \"to\": 4922}, {\"ngram\": \"an athletic component\", \"from\": 4935, \"to\": 4956}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So I can see the attraction, it being on that stage, but there wasn't a community component to it on the way there [to the Olympics].\", \"from\": 4986, \"to\": 5119, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the attraction\", \"from\": 4999, \"to\": 5013}, {\"ngram\": \"that stage\", \"from\": 5027, \"to\": 5037}, {\"ngram\": \"a community component\", \"from\": 5056, \"to\": 5077}, {\"ngram\": \"the way\", \"from\": 5087, \"to\": 5094}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 5105, \"to\": 5117}]}, {\"sentence\": \"[But now] there is a lot of speculation about what went down.\", \"from\": 5121, \"to\": 5182, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 5140, \"to\": 5145}, {\"ngram\": \"speculation\", \"from\": 5149, \"to\": 5160}]}, {\"sentence\": \"[That breaking] is not being included in the 2028 Olympics because of what happened here.\", \"from\": 5183, \"to\": 5272, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"That breaking\", \"from\": 5184, \"to\": 5197}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2028 Olympics\", \"from\": 5224, \"to\": 5241}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's not true.\", \"from\": 5273, \"to\": 5289, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The LA committee already made the decision about it not being included.\", \"from\": 5290, \"to\": 5361, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The LA committee\", \"from\": 5290, \"to\": 5306}, {\"ngram\": \"the decision\", \"from\": 5320, \"to\": 5332}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Does not make sense because it was born here in America.\", \"from\": 5362, \"to\": 5418, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"sense\", \"from\": 5376, \"to\": 5381}, {\"ngram\": \"America\", \"from\": 5410, \"to\": 5417}]}, {\"sentence\": \"[In the Paris Olympics] I think a lot of compromises were made on the way, and it's why we have the fallout that we are having.\", \"from\": 5420, \"to\": 5547, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 5424, \"to\": 5442}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 5452, \"to\": 5457}, {\"ngram\": \"compromises\", \"from\": 5461, \"to\": 5472}, {\"ngram\": \"the way\", \"from\": 5486, \"to\": 5493}, {\"ngram\": \"the fallout\", \"from\": 5516, \"to\": 5527}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I like what I saw, but it was very clean cut.\", \"from\": 5549, \"to\": 5594, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"very clean cut\", \"from\": 5579, \"to\": 5593}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They wanted culture.\", \"from\": 5595, \"to\": 5615, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"culture\", \"from\": 5607, \"to\": 5614}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now, if you want culture, it's cute.\", \"from\": 5616, \"to\": 5652, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"culture\", \"from\": 5633, \"to\": 5640}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You had a boombox.\", \"from\": 5653, \"to\": 5671, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a boombox\", \"from\": 5661, \"to\": 5670}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I like that you had the vinyl in the middle.\", \"from\": 5672, \"to\": 5716, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the vinyl\", \"from\": 5692, \"to\": 5701}, {\"ngram\": \"the middle\", \"from\": 5705, \"to\": 5715}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We would have had graffiti artists do up that boombox.\", \"from\": 5717, \"to\": 5771, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"graffiti artists\", \"from\": 5735, \"to\": 5751}, {\"ngram\": \"that boombox\", \"from\": 5758, \"to\": 5770}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I would have had breakers come out of the tape deck, coming down into a ramp out of the radio.\", \"from\": 5772, \"to\": 5866, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"breakers\", \"from\": 5789, \"to\": 5797}, {\"ngram\": \"the tape deck\", \"from\": 5810, \"to\": 5823}, {\"ngram\": \"a ramp\", \"from\": 5842, \"to\": 5848}, {\"ngram\": \"the radio\", \"from\": 5856, \"to\": 5865}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I would have had LL Cool J KRS-One as part of the ceremony.\", \"from\": 5867, \"to\": 5926, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5884, \"end\": 5893, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LL_Cool_J\", \"score\"