this fuel\", \"from\": 6502, \"to\": 6511}, {\"ngram\": \"a young lady\", \"from\": 6526, \"to\": 6538}, {\"ngram\": \"the name\", \"from\": 6542, \"to\": 6550}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What will be left over are the champions that took home medals, the ones who made an incredible impression on that dance floor.\", \"from\": 6562, \"to\": 6689, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the champions\", \"from\": 6589, \"to\": 6602}, {\"ngram\": \"home medals\", \"from\": 6613, \"to\": 6624}, {\"ngram\": \"the ones\", \"from\": 6626, \"to\": 6634}, {\"ngram\": \"an incredible impression\", \"from\": 6644, \"to\": 6668}, {\"ngram\": \"that dance floor\", \"from\": 6672, \"to\": 6688}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Al Jazeera: What do you think of Raygun's performance?\", \"from\": 6691, \"to\": 6745, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6724, \"end\": 6730, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.004313683775049e-55, \"text\": \"Raygun\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Rokafella: We watched the battle [breakdancing competition] live, but we have watched many battles, sometimes in person, sometimes with one of our dancers, our b-girls, competing.\", \"from\": 6747, \"to\": 6926, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Rokafella\", \"from\": 6747, \"to\": 6756}, {\"ngram\": \"the battle\", \"from\": 6769, \"to\": 6779}, {\"ngram\": \"competition\", \"from\": 6794, \"to\": 6805}, {\"ngram\": \"many battles\", \"from\": 6833, \"to\": 6845}, {\"ngram\": \"person\", \"from\": 6860, \"to\": 6866}, {\"ngram\": \"our dancers\", \"from\": 6890, \"to\": 6901}, {\"ngram\": \"our b-girls\", \"from\": 6903, \"to\": 6914}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The kangaroo hop, that was a surprise.\", \"from\": 6928, \"to\": 6966, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The kangaroo hop\", \"from\": 6928, \"to\": 6944}, {\"ngram\": \"a surprise\", \"from\": 6955, \"to\": 6965}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, what I am trying to get at is that in b-girl battles occasionally, but more often than not, you will get dancers who are not at a high skill level.\", \"from\": 6968, \"to\": 7124, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"b-girl battles\", \"from\": 7015, \"to\": 7029}, {\"ngram\": \"dancers\", \"from\": 7082, \"to\": 7089}, {\"ngram\": \"a high skill level\", \"from\": 7105, \"to\": 7123}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In general, we all have to work hard and we have to train.\", \"from\": 7125, \"to\": 7183, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In general, we are doing the same steps, but mentally, physically, there is a lot of differences here.\", \"from\": 7184, \"to\": 7286, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the same steps\", \"from\": 7209, \"to\": 7223}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 7260, \"to\": 7265}, {\"ngram\": \"differences\", \"from\": 7269, \"to\": 7280}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And so when people want to criticise her performance, we trust that the judges will see what we are seeing.\", \"from\": 7288, \"to\": 7395, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 7300, \"to\": 7306}, {\"ngram\": \"her performance\", \"from\": 7325, \"to\": 7340}, {\"ngram\": \"the judges\", \"from\": 7356, \"to\": 7366}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And no, she does not get to move to the next bracket, so we trust that.\", \"from\": 7396, \"to\": 7467, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the next bracket\", \"from\": 7432, \"to\": 7448}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kwikstep: My initial reaction when I saw Raygun was, how did she make it into this, to begin with?\", \"from\": 7469, \"to\": 7567, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7510, \"end\": 7516, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.004313683775049e-55, \"text\": \"Raygun\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My initial reaction\", \"from\": 7479, \"to\": 7498}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What were the checks and balances?\", \"from\": 7568, \"to\": 7602, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the checks\", \"from\": 7578, \"to\": 7588}, {\"ngram\": \"balances\", \"from\": 7593, \"to\": 7601}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In every event, there is people in last place, but nobody's focusing on that for days and days, making it into memes.\", \"from\": 7603, \"to\": 7720, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"every event\", \"from\": 7606, \"to\": 7617}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 7628, \"to\": 7634}, {\"ngram\": \"last place\", \"from\": 7638, \"to\": 7648}, {\"ngram\": \"nobody\", \"from\": 7654, \"to\": 7660}, {\"ngram\": \"days\", \"from\": 7684, \"to\": 7688}, {\"ngram\": \"days\", \"from\": 7693, \"to\": 7697}, {\"ngram\": \"memes\", \"from\": 7714, \"to\": 7719}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And they are on talk shows and all of that kind of stuff.\", \"from\": 7721, \"to\": 7778, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"talk shows\", \"from\": 7737, \"to\": 7747}, {\"ngram\": \"that kind\", \"from\": 7759, \"to\": 7768}, {\"ngram\": \"stuff\", \"from\": 7772, \"to\": 7777}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Let me give you an example.\", \"from\": 7780, \"to\": 7807, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an example\", \"from\": 7796, \"to\": 7806}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So I have a young man who called me, and he was almost in, I can say, in tears.\", \"from\": 7808, \"to\": 7887, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a young man\", \"from\": 7818, \"to\": 7829}, {\"ngram\": \"tears\", \"from\": 7881, \"to\": 7886}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His voice was shaking because he owns a school teaching breaking in a rural area.\", \"from\": 7888, \"to\": 7969, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"His voice\", \"from\": 7888, \"to\": 7897}, {\"ngram\": \"a school teaching\", \"from\": 7926, \"to\": 7943}, {\"ngram\": \"a rural area\", \"from\": 7956, \"to\": 7968}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And parents came in and said, \\\"Teach my kids the kangaroo.\\\"\", \"from\": 7971, \"to\": 8030, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"parents\", \"from\": 7975, \"to\": 7982}, {\"ngram\": \"my kids\", \"from\": 8008, \"to\": 8015}, {\"ngram\": \"the kangaroo\", \"from\": 8016, \"to\": 8028}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And he said, \\\"Please do not come in here and say that to me.\", \"from\": 8031, \"to\": 8091, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's very disrespectful.\\\"\", \"from\": 8092, \"to\": 8117, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They did not listen.\", \"from\": 8118, \"to\": 8138, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Now they have been asking him to teach their kids the kangaroo and sending him memes.\", \"from\": 8139, \"to\": 8224, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their kids\", \"from\": 8178, \"to\": 8188}, {\"ngram\": \"the kangaroo\", \"from\": 8189, \"to\": 8201}, {\"ngram\": \"memes\", \"from\": 8218, \"to\": 8223}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He called me, said, \\\"I do not know what to do because I think I am going to lose all my students and their parents because this is all they want.\\\"\", \"from\": 8225, \"to\": 8371, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all my students\", \"from\": 8306, \"to\": 8321}, {\"ngram\": \"their parents\", \"from\": 8326, \"to\": 8339}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To take this culture and beat somebody up with it, is not the right thing to do.\", \"from\": 8373, \"to\": 8453, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this culture\", \"from\": 8381, \"to\": 8393}, {\"ngram\": \"somebody\", \"from\": 8403, \"to\": 8411}, {\"ngram\": \"the right thing\", \"from\": 8431, \"to\": 8446}]}, {\"sentence\": \"byKwikstep And I told him, if you lose all of them, it's time for you to do something else.\", \"from\": 8455, \"to\": 8547, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"byKwikstep\", \"from\": 8455, \"to\": 8465}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 8512, \"to\": 8516}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 8531, \"to\": 8540}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Because they were not loyal to you to begin with.\", \"from\": 8548, \"to\": 8597, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If they had empathy, they would understand you and say, you know what?\", \"from\": 8598, \"to\": 8668, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"empathy\", \"from\": 8610, \"to\": 8617}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You are right, I am wrong.\", \"from\": 8669, \"to\": 8695, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And remind people that this dance is about Souljahs [a reference to Kwikstep's and Roka's Bronx based non-profit organization] in the trenches.\", \"from\": 8696, \"to\": 8839, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8779, \"end\": 8783, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roka,_Cambodia\", \"score\": 0.8421987811656587, \"rank\": 0.13636363636370238, \"text\": \"Roka\", \"types\": [\"Q532\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roka,_Cambodia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roka,_Cambodia\"}, {\"begin\": 8786, \"end\": 8791, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Bronx\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4385188955364397e-25, \"text\": \"Bronx\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Bronx\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Bronx\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 8707, \"to\": 8713}, {\"ngram\": \"this dance\", \"from\": 8719, \"to\": 8729}, {\"ngram\": \"Souljahs\", \"from\": 8739, \"to\": 8747}, {\"ngram\": \"[a reference\", \"from\": 8748, \"to\": 8760}, {\"ngram\": \"the trenches\", \"from\": 8826, \"to\": 8838}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If you look at the headlines at that time, it said, \\\"New York can drop dead.\\\"\", \"from\": 8841, \"to\": 8918, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8894, \"end\": 8902, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.807563978158262e-18, \"text\": \"New York\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the headlines\", \"from\": 8856, \"to\": 8869}, {\"ngram\": \"that time\", \"from\": 8873, \"to\": 8882}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They left us for dead, literally.\", \"from\": 8919, \"to\": 8952, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 8929, \"to\": 8931}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And post-civil rights, where I watched leaders get assassinated, I am listening to rhymes that say \\\"I am a somebody\\\" and I am cognisant that that comes from what?\", \"from\": 8953, \"to\": 9115, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"post-civil rights\", \"from\": 8957, \"to\": 8974}, {\"ngram\": \"leaders\", \"from\": 8992, \"to\": 8999}, {\"ngram\": \"rhymes\", \"from\": 9036, \"to\": 9042}, {\"ngram\": \"a somebody\", \"from\": 9058, \"to\": 9068}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Civil rights marches.\", \"from\": 9116, \"to\": 9137, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Civil rights marches\", \"from\": 9116, \"to\": 9136}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am somebody.\", \"from\": 9138, \"to\": 9152, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"somebody\", \"from\": 9143, \"to\": 9151}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And so when you have all of this happening in my mind and in my soul now, here I come to watch the Olympics, and I am watching people at the top of their game.\", \"from\": 9154, \"to\": 9313, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my mind\", \"from\": 9200, \"to\": 9207}, {\"ngram\": \"my soul\", \"from\": 9215, \"to\": 9222}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 9249, \"to\": 9261}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 9281, \"to\": 9287}, {\"ngram\": \"the top\", \"from\": 9291, \"to\": 9298}, {\"ngram\": \"their game\", \"from\": 9302, \"to\": 9312}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Some things are missing, but I am like, it's cool.\", \"from\": 9314, \"to\": 9364, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Some things\", \"from\": 9314, \"to\": 9325}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The movement is what I am watching.\", \"from\": 9365, \"to\": 9400, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The movement\", \"from\": 9365, \"to\": 9377}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is not just about moves.\", \"from\": 9401, \"to\": 9430, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"moves\", \"from\": 9424, \"to\": 9429}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's about the movement of the people.\", \"from\": 9431, \"to\": 9469, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the movement\", \"from\": 9442, \"to\": 9454}, {\"ngram\": \"the people\", \"from\": 9458, \"to\": 9468}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But then they chose to focus on her instead of, you know, Logistx or Sunny or Nicka, for that matter, who's killing the game.\", \"from\": 9471, \"to\": 9596, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Nicka\", \"from\": 9549, \"to\": 9554}, {\"ngram\": \"that matter\", \"from\": 9560, \"to\": 9571}, {\"ngram\": \"the game\", \"from\": 9587, \"to\": 9595}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They were incredible.\", \"from\": 9597, \"to\": 9618, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And so you take away all the momentum to focus on this one person who does not have the skillset.\", \"from\": 9619, \"to\": 9716, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all the momentum\", \"from\": 9640, \"to\": 9656}, {\"ngram\": \"this one person\", \"from\": 9669, \"to\": 9684}, {\"ngram\": \"the skillset\", \"from\": 9703, \"to\": 9715}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But it's almost like a knee-jerk instinct to make a parody of a Black and Brown dance, because that's what you were taught how to do.\", \"from\": 9717, \"to\": 9850, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a knee-jerk instinct\", \"from\": 9738, \"to\": 9758}, {\"ngram\": \"a parody\", \"from\": 9767, \"to\": 9775}, {\"ngram\": \"a Black and Brown dance\", \"from\": 9779, \"to\": 9802}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's not cool.\", \"from\": 9851, \"to\": 9867, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And I really feel bad for Raygun and what she has to deal with, because mental health is a real thing.\", \"from\": 9869, \"to\": 9971, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9895, \"end\": 9901, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.004313683775049e-55, \"text\": \"Raygun\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"mental health\", \"from\": 9941, \"to\": 9954}, {\"ngram\": \"a real thing\", \"from\": 9958, \"to\": 9970}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And as a community, we come from a place where we are mentally up against the wall, and this dance and music healed us.\", \"from\": 9972, \"to\": 10091, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a community\", \"from\": 9979, \"to\": 9990}, {\"ngram\": \"a place\", \"from\": 10005, \"to\": 10012}, {\"ngram\": \"the wall\", \"from\": 10046, \"to\": 10054}, {\"ngram\": \"this dance\", \"from\": 10060, \"to\": 10070}, {\"ngram\": \"music\", \"from\": 10075, \"to\": 10080}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 10088, \"to\": 10090}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And so to turn around and take this very same culture and beat somebody up with it is not the right thing to do.\", \"from\": 10092, \"to\": 10204, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this very same culture\", \"from\": 10123, \"to\": 10145}, {\"ngram\": \"somebody\", \"from\": 10155, \"to\": 10163}, {\"ngram\": \"the right thing\", \"from\": 10182, \"to\": 10197}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Al Jazeera: Tell us a bit about how breaking evolved.\", \"from\": 10206, \"to\": 10259, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 10223, \"to\": 10225}, {\"ngram\": \"a bit\", \"from\": 10226, \"to\": 10231}, {\"ngram\": \"how breaking\", \"from\": 10238, \"to\": 10250}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kwikstep:So breaking, in its first incarnation, started in the early 1970s \\u2026 We were fortunate enough to be exposed to Lindy Hop [on TV] - it's a dance that comes from the African-American contingent that was being done to swing music.\", \"from\": 10261, \"to\": 10496, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10380, \"end\": 10389, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lindy_Hop\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lindy Hop\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lindy_Hop\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lindy_Hop\"}, {\"begin\": 10433, \"end\": 10449, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/African-American_music\", \"score\": 0.9847234888764322, \"rank\": 0.013364452376735326, \"text\": \"African-American\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/African-American_music\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/African-American_music\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"its first incarnation\", \"from\": 10286, \"to\": 10307}, {\"ngram\": \"the early 1970s\", \"from\": 10320, \"to\": 10335}, {\"ngram\": \"TV\", \"from\": 10394, \"to\": 10396}, {\"ngram\": \"a dance\", \"from\": 10405, \"to\": 10412}, {\"ngram\": \"swing music\", \"from\": 10484, \"to\": 10495}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Rokafella: In the 1930s.\", \"from\": 10498, \"to\": 10522, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Rokafella\", \"from\": 10498, \"to\": 10507}, {\"ngram\": \"the 1930s\", \"from\": 10512, \"to\": 10521}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kwikstep: And you had jazz, swing, bebop music.\", \"from\": 10524, \"to\": 10571, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Kwikstep\", \"from\": 10524, \"to\": 10532}, {\"ngram\": \"jazz, swing, bebop music\", \"from\": 10546, \"to\": 10570}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And you listen to the word bebop, it sounds a lot like hip-hop.\", \"from\": 10572, \"to\": 10635, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the word bebop\", \"from\": 10590, \"to\": 10604}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 10616, \"to\": 10621}, {\"ngram\": \"hip-hop\", \"from\": 10627, \"to\": 10634}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And when people say, let us go to the hop, that's like saying, let us go to the jam.\", \"from\": 10636, \"to\": 10720, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 10645, \"to\": 10651}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 10661, \"to\": 10663}, {\"ngram\": \"the hop\", \"from\": 10670, \"to\": 10677}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 10703, \"to\": 10705}, {\"ngram\": \"the jam\", \"from\": 10712, \"to\": 10719}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So Lindy Hop swing, there is a clip called hell is a popping.\", \"from\": 10722, \"to\": 10783, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a clip\", \"from\": 10751, \"to\": 10757}, {\"ngram\": \"hell\", \"from\": 10765, \"to\": 10769}, {\"ngram\": \"a popping\", \"from\": 10773, \"to\": 10782}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When you look at this footage, see the video?\", \"from\": 10785, \"to\": 10830, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this footage\", \"from\": 10802, \"to\": 10814}, {\"ngram\": \"the video\", \"from\": 10820, \"to\": 10829}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That energy is like breaking energy, but it's not breaking.\", \"from\": 10831, \"to\": 10890, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"That energy\", \"from\": 10831, \"to\": 10842}, {\"ngram\": \"energy\", \"from\": 10860, \"to\": 10866}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When you look at it like that - you know - shuffling in the sand and being quiet and the chains come off.\", \"from\": 10892, \"to\": 10997, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the sand\", \"from\": 10948, \"to\": 10956}, {\"ngram\": \"the chains\", \"from\": 10977, \"to\": 10987}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now you are tapping sort of works and you hear, \\\"I am here.\\\"\", \"from\": 10998, \"to\": 11058, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"works\", \"from\": 11026, \"to\": 11031}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Nicholas Brothers, the Barry Brothers.\", \"from\": 11059, \"to\": 11101, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 11059, \"end\": 11080, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicholas_Brothers\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"The Nicholas Brothers\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicholas_Brothers\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicholas_Brothers\"}, {\"begin\": 11072, \"end\": 11080, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brother\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.61690269788756e-19, \"text\": \"Brothers\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brother\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brother\"}, {\"begin\": 11086, \"end\": 11091, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barry_Gibb\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.895279203612919e-26, \"text\": \"Barry\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barry_Gibb\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barry_Gibb\"}, {\"begin\": 11092, \"end\": 11100, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brother\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.61690269788756e-19, \"text\": \"Brothers\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brother\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brother\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's like watching your aunt move her hips while she's cooking.\", \"from\": 11103, \"to\": 11166, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your aunt\", \"from\": 11122, \"to\": 11131}, {\"ngram\": \"her hips\", \"from\": 11137, \"to\": 11145}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There is a sense of ancestry and knowledge being passed down to you.\", \"from\": 11167, \"to\": 11235, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a sense\", \"from\": 11176, \"to\": 11183}, {\"ngram\": \"ancestry\", \"from\": 11187, \"to\": 11195}, {\"ngram\": \"knowledge\", \"from\": 11200, \"to\": 11209}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When you look at hip-hop, it's like rock and roll.\", \"from\": 11237, \"to\": 11287, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"hip-hop\", \"from\": 11254, \"to\": 11261}, {\"ngram\": \"rock\", \"from\": 11273, \"to\": 11277}, {\"ngram\": \"roll\", \"from\": 11282, \"to\": 11286}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You are rocking and you are rolling to that rhythm.\", \"from\": 11288, \"to\": 11339, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that rhythm\", \"from\": 11327, \"to\": 11338}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Rhythm and blues, we are doing these rhythms because of the blues.\", \"from\": 11340, \"to\": 11406, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"these rhythms\", \"from\": 11371, \"to\": 11384}, {\"ngram\": \"the blues\", \"from\": 11396, \"to\": 11405}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When I look at the African-American dynamics and Afro-Caribbean dynamics, and when we saw one another.\", \"from\": 11408, \"to\": 11510, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 11427, \"end\": 11443, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/African-American_music\", \"score\": 0.9847234888764322, \"rank\": 0.013364452376735326, \"text\": \"African-American\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/African-American_music\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/African-American_music\"}, {\"begin\": 11457, \"end\": 11471, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Black_people\", \"score\": 0.9999999999336069, \"rank\": 6.520999893010995e-11, \"text\": \"Afro-Caribbean\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Black_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Black_people\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"When hip-hop was being born, before it was called hip-hop, there was a social exchange happening.\", \"from\": 11511, \"to\": 11608, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"hip-hop\", \"from\": 11516, \"to\": 11523}, {\"ngram\": \"hip-hop\", \"from\": 11561, \"to\": 11568}, {\"ngram\": \"a social exchange\", \"from\": 11580, \"to\": 11597}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You are watching Lindy Hop, you are watching swing music, you are watching the big bands, you are watching tap, and you go down with these moves in your head, and now you are rocking to this music that's jazz, It's disco, it's funk, but it's the highest part of the music called break beats.\", \"from\": 11610, \"to\": 11901, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 11627, \"end\": 11636, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lindy_Hop\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lindy Hop\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lindy_Hop\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lindy_Hop\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"swing music\", \"from\": 11655, \"to\": 11666}, {\"ngram\": \"the big bands\", \"from\": 11685, \"to\": 11698}, {\"ngram\": \"tap\", \"from\": 11717, \"to\": 11720}, {\"ngram\": \"these moves\", \"from\": 11743, \"to\": 11754}, {\"ngram\": \"your head\", \"from\": 11758, \"to\": 11767}, {\"ngram\": \"this music\", \"from\": 11796, \"to\": 11806}, {\"ngram\": \"jazz\", \"from\": 11814, \"to\": 11818}, {\"ngram\": \"disco\", \"from\": 11825, \"to\": 11830}, {\"ngram\": \"funk\", \"from\": 11837, \"to\": 11841}, {\"ngram\": \"the highest part\", \"from\": 11852, \"to\": 11868}, {\"ngram\": \"the music\", \"from\": 11872, \"to\": 11881}, {\"ngram\": \"break beats\", \"from\": 11889, \"to\": 11900}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And you are actually reliving through your ancestry in the moment, doing similar moves.\", \"from\": 11902, \"to\": 11989, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your ancestry\", \"from\": 11940, \"to\": 11953}, {\"ngram\": \"the moment\", \"from\": 11957, \"to\": 11967}, {\"ngram\": \"similar moves\", \"from\": 11975, \"to\": 11988}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Rokafella: The phase of the civil rights movement which also bled into Puerto Ricans standing and marching right there with the Black Panthers in New York City.\", \"from\": 11991, \"to\": 12151, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 12062, \"end\": 12075, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Puerto_Ricans\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.143793793631824e-14, \"text\": \"Puerto Ricans\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Puerto_Ricans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Puerto_Ricans\"}, {\"begin\": 12119, \"end\": 12133, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Black_Panther_Party\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1287046154048605e-29, \"text\": \"Black Panthers\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Black_Panther_Party\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Black_Panther_Party\"}, {\"begin\": 12137, \"end\": 12150, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.032981837839664e-29, \"text\": \"New York City\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Rokafella\", \"from\": 11991, \"to\": 12000}, {\"ngram\": \"The phase\", \"from\": 12002, \"to\": 12011}, {\"ngram\": \"the civil rights movement\", \"from\": 12015, \"to\": 12040}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So we were coming out of this and we were trying to find respect from our city officials and the government and at large.\", \"from\": 12152, \"to\": 12273, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"respect\", \"from\": 12209, \"to\": 12216}, {\"ngram\": \"our city officials\", \"from\": 12222, \"to\": 12240}, {\"ngram\": \"the government\", \"from\": 12245, \"to\": 12259}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And our leaders were assassinated.\", \"from\": 12275, \"to\": 12309, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our leaders\", \"from\": 12279, \"to\": 12290}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So we both marched together, and we both had to cope and endure the aftermath of that.\", \"from\": 12310, \"to\": 12396, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \